- `references/java-sdk/src/test/java/blue/language/sdk/dsl/DocBuilderGeneralDslParityTest.java`
  - `onEventMatchesYamlDefinition`
  - `onNamedEventMatchesYamlDefinition`
  - `onDocChangeMatchesYamlDefinition`
